ReadCaseAssignment1
data.value: select EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SPD_ID, OFF_ID, OSP_CODE, OSP_DATE, CAS_NO from CKT_ASSIGN_CASE with(readuncommitted) where @casNo = CAS_NO and EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @discontinueDate order by EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: ReadCaseAssignment2

data.name: ReadCaseRoleCase1
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T1.EMANCIPATION_DT, T2.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, T2.NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 with(readuncommitted) on @cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER and T1.TYPE = 'CH' and T1.START_DATE <= @startDate and T1.END_DATE >= @endDate

data.name: ReadCaseRoleCase2
data.value: select T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.TYPE, T1.CASE_ROLE_ID, T1.START_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T1.EMANCIPATION_DT, T2.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, T2.NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_CASE_ROLE T1 with(readuncommitted) on @cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.NUMB = T1.CAS_NUMBER and T1.TYPE = 'CH' and T1.START_DATE <= @startDate and T1.END_DATE >= @endDate

data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadCsePerson
data.value: select distinct T1.NUMB, T1.TYPE, T1.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK, T1.PAT_ESTAB_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON T1 with(readuncommitted) where T1.PAT_ESTAB_IND = 'Y' and T1.OUT_OF_WEDLOCK = 'Y' and T1.NUMB > @numb and exists ( select * from CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) where T1.NUMB = T2.CSP_NUMBER and T2.TYPE = 'CH' and T2.START_DATE <= @startDate and T2.END_DATE >= @endDate ) order by T1.NUMB

data.name: ReadGoodCauseCaseRoleGoodCause1
data.value: select * from ( select T1.CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CRO_TYPE, T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER, T2.START_DATE, T2.END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_GOOD_CAUSE T1 with(readuncommitted) on T1.CODE = 'GC' and T2.CAS_NUMBER = T1.CAS_NUMBER and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.TYPE = T1.CRO_TYPE and T2.CASE_ROLE_ID = T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER and T2.TYPE = 'AR' and @casNumber = T2.CAS_NUMBER and T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate and T2.START_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T2.END_DATE >= @effectiveDate ) S1 outer apply ( select top(1) CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_IDENTIFIER from CKT_GOOD_CAUSE where S1.CAS_NUMBER = CAS_NUMBER and S1.CSP_NUMBER = CSP_NUMBER and S1.CRO_TYPE = CRO_TYPE and S1.CRO_IDENTIFIER = CRO_IDENTIFIER and CODE = 'CO' and CREATED_TIMESTAMP > S1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP and CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp ) S2

data.name: ReadGoodCauseCaseRoleGoodCause2
data.value: select * from ( select T1.CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CAS_NUMBER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CRO_TYPE, T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER, T2.START_DATE, T2.END_DATE from CKT_CASE_ROLE T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_GOOD_CAUSE T1 with(readuncommitted) on T1.CODE = 'GC' and T2.CAS_NUMBER = T1.CAS_NUMBER and T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER and T2.TYPE = T1.CRO_TYPE and T2.CASE_ROLE_ID = T1.CRO_IDENTIFIER and T2.TYPE = 'AR' and @casNumber = T2.CAS_NUMBER and T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate and T2.START_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T2.END_DATE >= @effectiveDate ) S1 outer apply ( select top(1) CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, CAS_NUMBER, CSP_NUMBER, CRO_TYPE, CRO_IDENTIFIER from CKT_GOOD_CAUSE where S1.CAS_NUMBER = CAS_NUMBER and S1.CSP_NUMBER = CSP_NUMBER and S1.CRO_TYPE = CRO_TYPE and S1.CRO_IDENTIFIER = CRO_IDENTIFIER and CODE = 'CO' and CREATED_TIMESTAMP > S1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP and CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp ) S2

data.name: ReadOcse157Data
data.value: select FISCAL_YEAR, RUN_NUMBER, LINE_NUMBER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, NUMBER from CKT_OCSE157_DATA where FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear and LINE_NUMBER = @lineNumber order by RUN_NUMBER desc

data.name: ReadOcse157VerificationCsePerson
data.value: select * from ( select FISCAL_YEAR, RUN_NUMBER, LINE_NUMBER, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER from CKT_OCSE157_VERIFI with(readuncommitted) where FISCAL_YEAR = @fiscalYear and RUN_NUMBER = @runNumber and LINE_NUMBER = @lineNumber and SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER > @suppPersonNumber ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) NUMB, TYPE, OUT_OF_WEDLOCK, PAT_ESTAB_IND from CKT_CSE_PERSON where NUMB = S1.SUPP_PERSON_NUMBER ) S2
